                Eovia Carrara v4.1.1 Pro (C) Eovia Corporation
   
   Carrara 4 Pro software keeps  professional designers ahead of the  curve
   by  offering superior  performance capabilities  and an  extraordinarily
   abundant toolset. 

   Carrara 4 Pro has the  same competencies and highly intuitive  interface
   as  our  Standard  version  but adds  advanced  features  such  as sound
   support, 3D and vector motion blur, blurry reflections, extended  import
   capabilities and more.

   Carrara 4 Pro also comes pre-loaded with essential  plug-ins, TransPoser
   and  CADstyle, as well as  a fully functional version of  Amapi Designer
   7, our versatile modeling package.

   Additionally, the Eovia Chain  Network Rendering feature delivers  ultra
   -fast image and animation rendering by distributing tasks across a local
   network of up to five computers. 

   
   Key Features
   ------------
   Illustrators
   Carrara 4 Pro will help you take your illustration work to a new  level.
   Start in Adobe Illustrator and finish in the 3D environment of Carrara 4
   Pro. Your  illustrations will  have a  depth and  life that  is just not
   possible  in  a  2D  space.  With  lighting,  texturing  and   rendering
   capabilities unmatched at this  affordable price, Carrara 4  will change
   the way you realize your artistic dreams.	 	

   Animators and Modelers
   Carrara 4 Pro  delivers the advanced  tools that professional  animators
   and  modelers are  looking for.  It ships  with a  full license  of the
   powerful Amapi Designer 7  modeling application, providing a  robust and
   complete  3D  solution.  With advanced  workflow  features  like Network
   Rendering and new importers,  Carrara 4 Pro will  enable you to be  more
   productive and creative than ever before.	
	 	
   Multimedia Producers
   Whether youíre doing corporate video production, designing DVD menus, or
   creating  compelling intros  or promos,  your work  can be  enhanced by
   adding 3D. Carrara 4 Pro, with its easy-to-learn interface and  plethora
   of importers and exporters, will quickly fit in to your production cycle
   and deliver results that will enable you to improve your final products.
   Stop sending pieces of projects to other artists ñ keep it in-house  and
   increase your billables!	
 	 	 	
   CAD Designers
   Carrara 4 Pro is the ideal solution for visualizing your CAD models. The
   integrated CADstyle plug-in provides a wealth of CAD importers to enable
   you to take advantage of the superior lighting, texturing and  rendering
   engine in Carrara turn those  models into compelling images that  can be
   used in presentations, brochures, posters, ads and more. 
   
   For more informations stream to:
   --------------------------------
   http://www.eovia.com/products/carrara_pro/carrara_pro.asp
